Use the standard library
This is how to circular_shift of x and shift:
  Remember that chars is toarray of tostring of x
  Remember that n is chars's length
  Remember that result is []
  Do this n times:
    Remember that i is diff of n and result's length
    Remember that i is diff of i and 1
    Remember that src is remainder of sum of i and shift and n
    Add result to item src in chars
  End do
  When shift is n, then:
    The answer is tostring of x
  But, if not:
    The answer is result
  End when
Now you know